        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20791461/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20791461/" class="">第112页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/little-bladder/" class=" " title="猫侦探费拉达菲">猫侦探费拉达菲</a>
                (若信贝多真实语 三生同听一楼钟)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20791461">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20791461/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p20791461-2.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">记得在哪儿看到个说法，说中文社科学术词汇有75%来自日文翻译……所以如果中国人搞语言民族主义的话。。。
 </span>
